    <item>
      <title>WSP 斥资 18 亿美元收购爱达荷州工程公司，押注能源转型</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/wsp-buys-idaho-engineering-firm-in-1-8-billion-energy-transition-bet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[工程公司 WSP Global Inc. 同意以 24.4 亿加元（18 亿美元）收购专注于能源业务的竞争对手 Power Engineers Inc.，并得到新加坡主权财富基金和三大加​​拿大养老基金的资金支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/wsp-buys-idaho-engineering-firm-in-1-8-billion-energy-transition-bet</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 22:19:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>必和必拓向矿工提供 28,900 美元奖金以避免铜矿罢工</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/bhp-offers-miners-28-900-bonus-to-avoid-strike-at-copper-site</link>
      <description><![CDATA[必和必拓集团 (BHP Group) 提出了一项提高工资的提议 — — 包括增加 28,900 美元的奖金 — — 以避免这家全球最大铜矿发生罢工，目前正在等待智利工会领导人的回应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/bhp-offers-miners-28-900-bonus-to-avoid-strike-at-copper-site</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 21:55:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>惠誉下调以色列评级，因加沙战争预计将持续至 2025 年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/israel-s-rating-cut-by-fitch-as-gaza-war-seen-lasting-into-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[惠誉评级将以色列的主权债务评级下调了一个等级，并维持对以色列信用状况的负面展望，因为持续的军事冲突对该国的公共财政造成压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/israel-s-rating-cut-by-fitch-as-gaza-war-seen-lasting-into-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 21:53:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
