      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 12:43:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>赞比亚重新开放刚果边境，此前争端导致铜出口受阻</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/zambia-congo-start-talks-to-end-spat-that-closed-border-key-to-copper-trade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据国家广播公司报道，赞比亚将于周二重新开放与刚果民主共和国的边境口岸，此前紧张局势导致世界第二大铜生产国上周末对出口实施封锁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/zambia-congo-start-talks-to-end-spat-that-closed-border-key-to-copper-trade</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 08:40:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
